{"tid":1392714,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"【支線任務】入黎了解下google點收廣告費","createTime":"2019-07-31T23:59:44.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-01T14:02:27.000Z","uid":205614,"like":70,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":19,"replies":[{"pid":"aeadf5284862e2ca116ff021e74a5fe9c5bef3b0","tid":1392714,"uid":205614,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T23:59:44.000Z","msg":"話說小妹呢排發現Google Search入面嘅廣告係<span style=\"color: red;\">PPC(Pay Per Click，按點擊收錢)</span>，所以大家平時得閒除咗推po之外，都可以一齊睇吓藍紅商家嘅廣告，唔好嘥哂佢地D廣告budget呀！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n首先同大家介紹下Google Ads呢個工具先(實際操作唔需要用到佢)，佢可以幫商戶喺google落廣告，增加暴光率。咁佢係點收費嫁呢？<br />\n<br />\n入去Google Ads &rarr; 工具和設定 &rarr; 策劃工具 &rarr; 關鍵字策劃工具，喺右邊輸入Keyword後，Google就會比D data你。<br />\n例如我search「社交媒體」，會見到呢個表。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/NDzPKTt.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FNDzPKTt.jpg&h=75952a62&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n咁啫係我用呢個Keyword落咗廣告後，<span style=\"color: red;\">每當一個人Click入我嘅網址，我就要比US$1.77=HKD$14 廣告費</span>(當然，呢個數只係一個參考，因為Google Ads背後仲有好多其他操作，而且唔同keywords都會有唔同價錢)<br />\n<br />\n去返Google search「社交媒體」，會見到result排頭嘅係大陸交友網廣告。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/4qf3Pkk.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F4qf3Pkk.jpg&h=1ce21b5f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n只要你click入去，呢個網址就要比$14 google嫁啦！<span style=\"color: red;\">大家click得越多，佢地比嘅廣告費越貴</span>，直到達到佢地每日/月嘅budget上限，廣告就會自動消失。所以大家要發掘多d potential keywords，一齊支持吓唔同企業！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n不過搵Keywords都要有技巧，例如你想搵吉X家嘅廣告，試下search牛肉飯，日式菜等同佢嘅product有關嘅詞，唔好直接打佢個名(可惜吉X家冇落廣告)。另外，用手機/電腦；平時嘅搜尋習慣等因素都會影響result，所以每個人見到嘅野未必相同。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n最後戴定頭盔先，小妹都係啱啱開始接觸呢個工具，唔肯定咁做會唔會為網頁帶黎其他正負面影響，求其他巴絲賜教。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">香港人 加油</span></span>"},{"pid":"e422ee1fc4fd182f5434a0573ee32721a8d79c23","tid":1392714,"uid":205614,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-01T00:05:48.000Z","msg":"自推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bouncer.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"30a6d5b20a02e9bb41c9a4b52a7705c17c0f998d","tid":1392714,"uid":205614,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-01T00:06:18.000Z","msg":"10"},{"pid":"3068d3312c93d9c24367d7cf9f51c615d63bb706","tid":1392714,"uid":205614,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-01T00:08:36.000Z","msg":"9"},{"pid":"4b49420ad98ca606c0855bf624e7ed6260e8aed7","tid":1392714,"uid":32261,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-01T00:10:11.000Z","msg":"終於有人講<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"93efe15768e02fb2fc4bc7c55c56165203b99714","tid":1392714,"uid":205614,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"4b49420ad98ca606c0855bf624e7ed6260e8aed7","tid":1392714,"uid":32261,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-01T00:10:11.000Z","msg":"終於有人講<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-01T00:12:57.000Z","msg":"巴打早晨<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"137fc7c4c399cccb03ff1b82d246a575b67dace8","tid":1392714,"uid":287422,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-01T00:19:28.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e79ee406db5cb9f48f960b3a66d96ec68ecfe1be","tid":1392714,"uid":72795,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-08-01T00:19:53.000Z","msg":"等IT同事出chrome extension, 自動按廣告<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"98587148077dc8a3dc372f2c1d4c91f9ef26f8ad","tid":1392714,"uid":205614,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"137fc